The Glenn Beck Program - 10/18/13


Friday, October 18, 2013 10:58 AM



Glenn goes back in time to hear from a man who's views mirror many American's,
 a man who changed the face of motion pictures.

  Also, another game of More On Trivia, this time pinning Indianapolis against Denver.

  Plus, a CNN reporter calls out the anchor for labeling Tea Partiers as radicals,

       and how Ted Cruz is not in D.C. to make friends.
